Behind the Madness, Before the Magic ✨🎭
This wasn’t possible without your support and guidance to my fav @chitrashetty @r.venterprises @arora_mudit 

This is where it all began — the chaos, the creation, the vision that refused to settle for anything less than ICONIC. From sketching styling boards to stitching together a dream, this look took half a month of non-stop hustle, creative bursts, breakdowns, breakthroughs, and a whole lot of blood, sweat & stardust 🔥

And now… it’s here to break the internet — because when we show up, we show up to own it all. 💥🔥
From head-to-toe styling to custom outfits — this grand carnival look is not just a moment. It’s a movement
